{
  "title": "Viết kịch bản trực quan",
  "html": "<main><header class=\"section-page-header\"><div class=\"row d-flex justify-content-between\"><div class=\"col col-sm-10\"></div><!----></div><!----><h1>Viết kịch bản trực quan</h1><p class=\"text-secondary mb-0\">Tổng quan về việc sử dụng hệ thống viết kịch bản trực quan Blueprint cho trò chơi.</p><!----></header><!----><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-9 print-w-100\"><div class=\"b-img\"><img class=\"unreal-doc-img\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Blueprints Visual Scripting\" width=\"1920\" height=\"335\" loading=\"lazy\" fetchpriority=\"auto\" decoding=\"auto\" ng-img=\"true\" src=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/community/api/documentation/image/89acb409-35d8-4c6c-b2da-b0f8048ec778?resizing_type=fill&amp;width=1920&amp;height=335\" srcset=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/community/api/documentation/image/89acb409-35d8-4c6c-b2da-b0f8048ec778?resizing_type=fill&amp;width=1920&amp;height=335 1x, https://dev.epicgames.com/community/api/documentation/image/89acb409-35d8-4c6c-b2da-b0f8048ec778?resizing_type=fill&amp;width=3840&amp;height=670 2x\"></div><!----><!----><!----><header class=\"document-header mb-3 d-lg-none d-print-none\"><content-nav class=\"content-nav is-collapsible\" ngh=\"6\"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></content-nav></header><!----><article><!----><!----><div document-content-blocks-renderer=\"\" class=\"d-block\" ngh=\"10\"><div id=\"content-blocks-renderer\" class=\"content-blocks-renderer\"><block-switch-control class=\"block-switch-control\" ngh=\"7\"><!----></block-switch-control><block-switch-info class=\"block-switch-info\" ngh=\"8\"><!----></block-switch-info><blocks-renderer id=\"blocks-renderer\" ngh=\"9\"><!----><block-markdown ngh=\"2\"><div class=\"block-markdown\"><block-excerpt-md id=\"intro\">\n<p>các<strong>Kịch bản trực quan Blueprint</strong>hệ thống trong Unreal Engine là một hệ thống viết kịch bản trò chơi hoàn chỉnh dựa trên khái niệm sử dụng\ngiao diện dựa trên nút để tạo các phần tử trò chơi từ bên trong Unreal Editor. Giống như nhiều ngôn ngữ kịch bản phổ biến, nó được sử dụng để xác định các lớp hoặc đối tượng hướng đối tượng (OO) trong công cụ.</p>\n\n<p>Hệ thống này cực kỳ linh hoạt và mạnh mẽ vì nó cung cấp khả năng cho các nhà thiết kế sử dụng hầu như đầy đủ các khái niệm và công cụ thường chỉ dành cho các lập trình viên. Ngoài ra,\nĐánh dấu dành riêng cho bản thiết kế có sẵn trong quá trình triển khai C++ của Unreal Engine cho phép các lập trình viên tạo ra các hệ thống cơ sở mà các nhà thiết kế có thể mở rộng.</p>\n</block-excerpt-md>\n\n<h2 id=\"gettingstarted\">Bắt đầu</h2>\n\n<p><block-dir-item-md description=\"Get up and running by creating your first Blueprint.\" href=\"#unreal-doc:quick-start-guide-for-blueprints-visual-scripting-in-unreal-engine\" page-name=\"Blueprints Quick Start Guide\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/958201ab-7025-4afc-b577-cb621a268545/quickstart.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>%programming-and-scripting/blueprints-visual-scripting/Bắt đầu/Tổng quan:Chủ đề%</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"generalscripting\">Kịch bản chung</h2>\n\n<p>%programming-and-scripting/blueprints-visual-scripting/Bắt đầu/Scripting:Chủ đề%</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"buildingblueprints\">Bản thiết kế xây dựng</h2>\n\n<p><block-dir-item-md description=\"The User Guide is the go-to source to learn the different parts of Blueprints and nodes that are available to use within Blueprint graphs.\" href=\"#unreal-doc:anatomy-of-a-blueprint-in-unreal-engine\" page-name=\"Anatomy of a Blueprint\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/28131e56-e00a-4310-910a-8c8799f4b429/anatomy.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"The User Guide is the go-to source to learn the different parts of Blueprints and nodes that are available to use within Blueprint graphs.\" href=\"#unreal-doc:specialized-blueprint-visual-scripting-node-groups-in-unreal-engine\" page-name=\"Specialized Blueprint Node Groups\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/2125c14e-5c38-4de0-9258-5ff865440462/using_interface_topic.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>%programming-and-scripting/blueprints-visual-scripting/BP_HowTo:Topic%<block-dir-item-md description=\"Reference covering Blueprint shortcuts and useful actions.\" href=\"#unreal-doc:blueprint-editor-cheat-sheet-in-unreal-engine\" page-name=\"Blueprint Editor Cheat Sheet\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/2edee1d9-e374-40ac-84fb-dd7b347e3997/blueprintcheatsheet.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"Tips and tricks to help you make decisions about when to use Blueprints and how best to set them up.\" href=\"#unreal-doc:blueprint-best-practices-in-unreal-engine\" page-name=\"Blueprint Best Practices\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/ce9e0d81-ae9f-4070-9dd2-5f044b51dbb9/bestpractices_topic.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md></p>\n\n<h2 id=\"blueprintcommunication\">Kế hoạch truyền thông</h2>\n\n<p><block-dir-item-md description=\"Overview of when to use different methods of Blueprint Communications.\" href=\"#unreal-doc:blueprint-communication-usage-in-unreal-engine\" page-name=\"Blueprint Communication Usage\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/fb61ed7b-926c-4740-90bd-dc33aed27951/bp_comms_topic.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"Allows a Blueprint Class to report on its state to the Level Blueprint.\" href=\"#unreal-doc:event-dispatchers-in-unreal-engine\" page-name=\"Event Dispatchers\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/3fa806fb-f88c-4663-a69e-c633132328e4/event_dispatcher_topic.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"Blueprints that declare functions to define an interface between Blueprints.\" href=\"#unreal-doc:blueprint-interface-in-unreal-engine\" page-name=\"Blueprint Interface\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/e53e400e-831a-4a0f-9990-6b9dd18d51e4/blueprint_interface.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md></p>\n\n<h2 id=\"topics\">chủ đề</h2>\n\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"Tips and tricks to help you make decisions about when to use Blueprints and how best to set them up.\" href=\"#unreal-doc:blueprint-best-practices-in-unreal-engine\" page-name=\"Blueprint Best Practices\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/ce9e0d81-ae9f-4070-9dd2-5f044b51dbb9/bestpractices_topic.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"An overview of Blueprint Namespaces.\" href=\"#unreal-doc:blueprint-namespaces-in-unreal-engine\" page-name=\"Blueprint Namespaces\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/e4c44c17-06f1-4d45-8533-bed9afd3971a/placeholder_topic.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"Introduction to visual scripting with Blueprints.\" href=\"#unreal-doc:introduction-to-blueprints-visual-scripting-in-unreal-engine\" page-name=\"Introduction to Blueprints\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/76193147-a1c9-4179-8528-95eb732b2ca5/intro_topic.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"The User Guide is the go-to source to learn the different parts of Blueprints and nodes that are available to use within Blueprint graphs.\" href=\"#unreal-doc:anatomy-of-a-blueprint-in-unreal-engine\" page-name=\"Anatomy of a Blueprint\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/28131e56-e00a-4310-910a-8c8799f4b429/anatomy.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"Pause Blueprint execution using Breakpoints to inspect graphs and the values of their variables.\" href=\"#unreal-doc:blueprint-debugger-in-unreal-engine\" page-name=\"Blueprint Debugger\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/965aecb5-6cf8-4d0a-bb2a-4c5593707e57/placeholder_topic.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n</div></block-markdown><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></blocks-renderer></div><!----></div></article><tags-list class=\"mt-1 d-print-none\" ngh=\"11\"><!----><ul class=\"labels-list is-links\"><li class=\"labels-item\"><!----><a class=\"labels-link\" href=\"/community/search?query=blueprints\">bản thiết kế</a><!----></li><!----></ul><!----></tags-list><!----><div class=\"col-lg-3 d-none d-lg-block d-print-none\"><!----></div></div><!----><!----><!----></main>",
